divs: Sighting DetailsTraveling north on prospect. Saw objects in the distance in front of the car. Pulled over to watch. Objects moved slowly and once they passed over us they became invisible. At 10pm it was very dark out side. Looked like lights in the sky, larger than a planet. They slowly moved accross
Summary: 21 objects moving from the NE to S. west Amber color
